# Copy to .env in ciri:/data/stacks/jellyfin/ and chmod 600.
#
# This stack currently needs NO .env values:
# - No secrets — Jellyfin's admin account is created in the web UI on first run
#   and stored in ./config, not here.
# - JELLYFIN_PublishedServerUrl is intentionally unset in compose.yaml (it broke
#   the Samsung TV's native player). If you ever re-enable it, add the env line
#   back in compose.yaml and set the URL here, e.g.:
#     JELLYFIN_PUBLISHED_URL=http://jellyfin.kaermorhen.internal:8096
